---
title: Swedish-Style Pork Meatballs & Creamy Bacon-Dill Sauce with Garlicky Greens, Cheesy Mash & Cherry Sauce
description: With two kinds of proteins: juicy pork and crispy bacon in the creamy sauce, these Swedish meatballs are pure comfort food. Add
a cheesy mash, with tart cherry sauce and greens and, you'll have a dish paying homage to the true Scandi spirit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/swedish-style-pork-meatballs-creamy-bacon-dill-sauce-d14e20ea.jpg
